mixin contactArea--en
	section.section.contact-section
		div.container
			h2.text-center.contact-section__heading We are dedicated to providing you the best service.
			p.text-center.description.description--narrow.contact-section__description If you are interested in our offerings, please leave your contact information and we will reach out to you.
			+link('contact-en', 'Contact Us')(class="btn btn-middle btn-default--outline contact-section__btn")

